Class ControllerSimulationMarketMenu

java.lang.Object
Controller.Controller
Controller.ControllerSimulation
Controller.ControllerSimulationMarketMenu
All Implemented Interfaces:
InterfaceController
public class ControllerSimulationMarketMenu extends ControllerSimulation
The ControllerSimulationMarketMenu class manages the interactions between the view and the simulation model for the market menu in the kiosk simulation.
